{"in": {"title": "Ode to an iPhone", "subtitle": "by katya raman, 2018", "lines": ["NARRATOR: O sacred golden iPhone in my hand,", "NARRATOR: O Portal to dimensions yet unknown:", "NARRATOR: These thoughts I'm sent like scribbles scrawled on sand,", "NARRATOR: On distant shores where stormy winds have blown,", "NARRATOR: Would all have died before my willing ears,", "NARRATOR: Could listen patiently to empathize,", "NARRATOR: With every concern - all your deepest fears,", "NARRATOR: To share those teardrops from your limpid eyes.", "NARRATOR: But by this magic, many miles away,", "NARRATOR: I cross the seven seas to be with you,", "NARRATOR: And we, together, just like yesterday,", "NARRATOR: Will brave your trying times to see them through,", "NARRATOR: Gone, the day when no one's nearby.", "NARRATOR: Gone, the lonely laugh, the silent cry."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Raveena", "SCENE": "Matthew", "TITLE": "Joanna", "SMALL VOICE": "Raveena", "FANGS": "Brian", "PEONY": "Raveena"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "968f2642d3ca042ce05c65e52e26bc71", "audio_objects": [["3ff1de7be5a396d55490995611dc854a-o-sacred-golden-iphone-in---", 0], ["068ecca94359c08ad6e9587da6102004-o-portal-to-dimensions-ye---", 0], ["0e87b33cac07128b0be9807189effb0f-these-thoughts-i-m-sent-l---", 0], ["82c285f10bd8a44914c028ccd355d3c0-on-distant-shores-where-s---", 0], ["5e33a824d690592f5d61822df863a7fc-would-all-have-died-befor---", 0], ["35b30793927de354a2fc40a68894d626-could-listen-patiently-to---", 0], ["833a1a4489ced81c10939918ef25d17a-with-every-concern---all----", 0], ["ac440d1ff81295012d818dc1bf40e98e-to-share-those-teardrops----", 0], ["b1aba0a6932e29d4f3bcf00709ff6933-but-by-this-magic--many-m---", 0], ["89683935f12bc49da23452a03738e29a-i-cross-the-seven-seas-to---", 0], ["992d18b4a9f36a38a7744f702eceba85-and-we--together--just-li---", 0], ["c19ceb23078dd32b9d9d1aed4c995177-will-brave-your-trying-ti---", 0], ["56f935b86b63d3382d973f208f329f6d-gone--the-day-when-no-one---", 0], ["18f4a8796ef3a